text: Wufengshania is an extinct genus of bothriolepidid Placoderm from the Emsian epoch of China. The type species, Wufengshania magniforaminis was named by Zhaohui Pan et al., 2018. ==Taxonomy== === Species === A single species of Wufengshania magniforaminis has been described so far. W magniforaminus' fossil remains are found in Emsian Late Devonian strata of China. ==See also== *List of placoderms ==References== Category:Antiarchi Category:Placoderms of Asia Category:Late Devonian first appearances Category:Late Devonian animals Category:Emsian extinctions Category:Fossil taxa described in 2018
